<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="id"><head><meta charset="UTF-8" /><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" /><title>OpenRelay — Kontroler Relay IoT Open Source</title><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" /><link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin /><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@300;400;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" /><link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" /></head><body>
  <nav><div class="nav-logo"><div class="nav-logo-mark"></div><div class="nav-title">OpenRelay</div></div><ul class="nav-links"><li><a href="#tentang">Tentang</a></li><li><a href="#fitur">Fitur</a></li><li><a href="#tim">Tim</a></li><li><a href="#akses">Akses</a></li></ul><a href="#" class="nav-cta">Unduh Dokumen</a></nav>
  <section class="hero"><div class="hero-badge"><div class="badge-dot"></div><span>IoT Ready</span></div><h1>Kontroler Relay IoT<br /><span class="amp">&amp;</span><span class="open">Open Source</span></h1><p class="hero-sub">Sistem kontrol relay berbasis ESP32 dengan dukungan WiFi, Bluetooth, dan jaringan mesh untuk automasi rumah dan industri</p><div class="hero-ctas"><a href="#" class="btn-primary">Lihat Spesifikasi</a><a href="#" class="btn-secondary">Unduh Dokumentasi</a></div></section>
  <section id="tentang" class="section"><div name="&#34;container&#34;"><h2>Tentang Proyek</h2><p>OpenRelay adalah proyek kontrol relay IoT open source yang dikembangkan untuk kompetisi FIKSI 2026. Sistem ini dirancang untuk memberikan solusi kontrol relay yang fleksibel, andal, dan mudah diintegrasikan dengan berbagai sistem automasi.</p><p>Dikembangkan oleh GT dan Muhammad Rizky Alfianno dari SMK Negeri 1 Madiun, OpenRelay menggunakan teknologi ESP32 dengan dukungan ekspander PCF8574 dan MCP23017 untuk mengontrol hingga 128 relay secara independen.</p></div></section>
  <section id="fitur" class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Fitur Utama</h2><div class="features-grid"><div class="feature-card"><h3>Kapasitas Tinggi</h3><p>Dukungan hingga 128 relay melalui kombinasi GPIO built-in ESP32 dan ekspander I2C (PCF8574, MCP23017)</p></div><div class="feature-card"><h3>Komunikasi Multikanal</h3><p>WiFi, Bluetooth, dan jaringan mesh untuk koneksi yang andal dalam berbagai lingkungan</p></div><div class="feature-card"><h3>Kontrol Lokal dan Jarak Jauh</h3><p>Akses melalui web UI lokal, MQTT, dan dashboard remote yang dihosting di GitHub Pages</p></div></div></div></section>
  <section id="stats" class="section-alt"><div class="container"><h2>Statistik Sistem</h2><div class="stats-grid"><div class="stat-card"><h3>128</h3><p>Relay Maksimum</p></div><div class="stat-card"><h3>99.9%</h3><p>Uptime Terjamin</p></div><div class="stat-card"><h3>1000</h3><p>Messages per Detik</p></div></div></div></section>
  <section id="rekayasa" class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Rekayasa Sistem</h2><div class="architecture-diagram"><h3>Arsitektur Sistem</h3><div class="diagram-components"><div class="component"><h4>ESP32 Core</h4><p>Microcontroller utama dengan WiFi/BT</p></div><div class="component"><h4>Expander I2C</h4><p>PCF8574 &amp; MCP23017 untuk I/O tambahan</p></div><div class="component"><h4>Penyimpanan</h4><p>LittleFS untuk konfigurasi dan UI</p></div><div class="component"><h4>Konektivitas</h4><p>WiFi, Bluetooth, dan jaringan mesh</p></div></div></div></div></section>
  <section id="alat" class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Alat dan Bahan</h2><div class="tools-grid"><div class="tool-card"><h4>ESP32 DevKit V4</h4><p>Papan pengembangan utama</p></div><div class="tool-card"><h4>PCF8574</h4><p>Ekspander I2C 8-bit</p></div><div class="tool-card"><h4>MCP23017</h4><p>Ekspander I2C 16-bit</p></div><div class="tool-card"><h4>Relay Module</h4><p>Modul relay 5V aktif-low</p></div><div class="tool-card"><h4>Kabel dan Konnektor</h4><p>Jumper, terminal block, dan konektor</p></div><div class="tool-card"><h4>PCB Custom</h4><p>Desain PCB khusus untuk prototipe</p></div></div></div></section>
  <section id="tim" class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Tim Pengembang</h2><div class="team-grid"><div class="team-member"><div class="member-avatar"></div><h3>GT</h3><p>Pengembang Utama</p><p>ESP32, Firmware, Elektronika</p></div><div class="team-member"><div class="member-avatar"></div><h3>M. Rizky Alfianno</h3><p>Pengembang Pendukung</p><p>Web UI, Dokumentasi, Presentasi</p></div></div></div></section>
  <section id="akses" class="section"><div class="container"><h2>Cara Mengakses Sistem</h2><div class="access-grid"><div class="access-card"><div class="access-icon">🎯</div><div class="access-title">ESP32 Native</div><div class="access-desc">Akses langsung melalui serial monitor atau interface web yang dijalankan pada ESP32 itu sendiri.</div><span class="access-url">http://esp32-device.local</span></div><div class="access-card"><div class="access-icon">🌐</div><div class="access-title">Remote Dashboard</div><div class="access-desc">Dashboard web siap pakai yang dihosting di GitHub Pages. Akses dan kontrol relay dari browser menggunakan MQTT over WSS. Tidak butuh instalasi.</div><span class="access-url">relay-remote-web (GitHub Pages)</span></div><div class="access-card"><div class="access-icon">📟</div><div class="access-title">Web UI Lokal</div><div class="access-desc">Akses dashboard lokal langsung dari ESP32 melalui HTTP ke IP perangkat. Tersimpan di LittleFS. Tersedia saat tidak ada koneksi internet.</div><span class="access-url">http://relaycrtl.local</span></div><div class="access-card"><div class="access-icon">📡</div><div class="access-title">MQTT Direct</div><div class="access-desc">Gunakan semua client MQTT yang mendukung (Home Assistant, Node-RED, MQTT Explorer, dsb) dengan prefix <code style="font-size:11px">home/relay</code>.</div><span class="access-url">broker.hivemq.com : 1883</span></div></div></div></section>
  <div style="margin-top: 48px; text-align: center;" class="reveal"><p style="color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px;">WiFi Access Point untuk setup pertama:</p><div style="display:inline-flex; gap:32px; background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding: 24px 40px;"><div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-dim); margin-bottom:4px;">SSID</div><div style="font-family:&quot;Chakra Petch&quot;,monospace; color:var(--amber); font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">ESP32-Relay</div></div><div style="width:1px; background:var(--border);"></div><div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-dim); margin-bottom:4px;">Password</div><div style="font-family:&quot;Chakra Petch&quot;,monospace; color:var(--amber); font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">relay1234</div></div><div style="width:1px; background:var(--border);"></div><div style="text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-dim); margin-bottom:4px;">OTA Password</div><div style="font-family:&quot;Chakra Petch&quot;,monospace; color:var(--amber); font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">relay_ota</div></div></div></div>
  <footer><div class="footer-inner"><div class="footer-logo"><div class="nav-logo-mark" style="width:28px;height:28px;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="width:16px;height:16px;"><rect x="3" y="9" width="18" height="6" rx="1" stroke="#07090f" stroke-width="2"/><circle cx="8" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#07090f"/><circle cx="16" cy="12" r="1.5" fill="#07090f"/><path d="M3 12H1M23 12H21M8 9V7M16 9V7M8 15V17M16 15V17" stroke="#07090f" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div><span style="font-family:&quot;Chakra Petch&quot;,monospace;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;">OpenRelay</span></div><p class="footer-copy">� 2026 &nbsp;GT & M. Rizky Alfianno &nbsp;� &nbsp;SMK Negeri 1 Madiun &nbsp;� &nbsp;FIKSI 2026</p><div class="footer-links"><a href="#tentang">Tentang</a><a href="#fitur">Fitur</a><a href="#tim">Tim</a><a href="#akses">Akses</a></div></div></footer><script>// Relay dot visualizer (function() { const vis = document.getElementById("relay-vis"); const total = 64; const dots = []; for (let i = 0; i < total; i++) { const d = document.createElement("div"); d.className = "relay-dot"; vis.appendChild(d); dots.push(d); } function animate() { const t = Date.now(); dots.forEach((d, i) => { const wave = Math.sin(t * 0.001 + i * 0.4); const on = wave > 0.3; const green = wave > 0.7; d.className = "relay-dot" + (on ? (green ? " green" : " on") : ""); }); requestAnimationFrame(animate); } animate(); })(); // Scroll reveal const reveals = document.querySelectorAll(".reveal"); const obs = new IntersectionObserver(entries => { entries.forEach(e => { if (e.isIntersecting) { e.target.classList.add("visible"); obs.unobserve(e.target); } }); }, { threshold: 0.12 }); reveals.forEach(r => obs.observe(r)); </script></body></html>